***************************************


1.first create hello.c file in folder
2.go to lkmpg link and paste hello world kernel module program
3.create makefile in that folder and copy the code and paste
4.compile the module using command ->make
5.chek the list of kernel module use command->lsmod modulename
6.use insmod command to insert module->insmod hello.ko
7.chek the list of kernel module use command->lsmod
*******you show your module name hello***********
8.check logfile message we use command ->dmesg
9.use rmmod command to remove the module ->rmmodmodulename
10.chek the list of kernel module use command->lsmod
*******Not showing your module name hello***********

